OL,3,CBritain's biggest police force to
OL,4,Cdouble use of live facial recognition
OL,6,FBritain's biggest police force is set
OL,7,Fto more than double its use of live
OL,8,Ffacial recognition to up to 10
OL,9,Fdeployments a week.
OL,11,FThe move by the Metropolitan Police
OL,12,Fcomes as it restructures to cover the
OL,13,Floss of 1,400 officers and 300 staff
OL,14,Famid budget shortages.
OL,16,FPart of the overhaul will also see
OL,17,Fofficers moved to bulk up the force's
OL,18,Fpublic order crime team, as the Met
OL,19,Fsaid it has faced increased demand
OL,20,Flinked to protest-related crimes in
OL,21,Fthe past two years.
