OL,6,FThe squad will go from 48 to 63
OL,7,Fofficers due to a rise in the number
OL,8,Fof protests, particularly related to
OL,9,FIsrael and Palestine, as well as
OL,10,Fenvironmental issues.
OL,12,FForce chief Sir Mark Rowley told the
OL,13,FPA news agency: "The numbers of
OL,14,Fprotests have grown over the last
OL,15,Fcouple of years.
OL,17,F"We don't have any powers that are
OL,18,Fthere to reduce the number of
OL,19,Fprotests, to cancel them.
