OL,6,F"Laws are very permissive and
OL,7,Fencouraging of protests, which is
OL,8,Fentirely understandable, and I've got
OL,9,Fno objection to that, but what we've
OL,10,Fseen, unfortunately, is a proportion
OL,11,Fof those create crime and offences."
OL,13,FAs part of the latest details of its
OL,14,Frestructure, the Met announced that
OL,15,Flive facial recognition will now be
OL,16,Fused up to 10 times per week across
OL,17,Ffive days, up from the current four
OL,18,Ftimes per week across two days.
