OL,6,F"Any tech which has the potential to
OL,7,Finfringe on our rights in the way
OL,8,Fscanning and identifying millions of
OL,9,Fpeople does needs to have robust
OL,10,Fsafeguards around its use, including
OL,11,Fensuring that proper independent
OL,12,Foversight is in place.
OL,14,F"The Government must legislate now to
OL,15,Fregulate this technology, protect
OL,16,Fpeople's rights, and make sure that
OL,17,Fthe law on facial recognition does not
OL,18,Fget outpaced by the use."
OL,20,FSir Mark insisted that the technology
OL,21,Fis responsibly used.
