OL,6,F"We're only using it to look for
OL,7,Fserious offenders like wanted
OL,8,Foffenders and registered sex offenders.
OL,10,F"We routinely put it out there and
OL,11,Fcapture multiple serious offenders in
OL,12,Fone go, many of whom have committed
OL,13,Fserious offences against women or
OL,14,Fchildren, or people who are wanted for
OL,15,Farmed robbery.
OL,17,F"It's a fantastic piece of technology.
OL,18,FIt's very responsibly used, and that's
OL,19,Fwhy most of the public support it."
